com.vmware.vcenter.crypto_manager.kms

Interface Providers

  • All Superinterfaces:
    com.vmware.vapi.internal.bindings.CompletionStageService, ProvidersTypes, Service
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    ProvidersStub

    public interface Providers
extends Service, ProvidersTypes, com.vmware.vapi.internal.bindings.CompletionStageService
    The Providers interface provides methods to create, retrieve, update, delete, export and import providers. This interface was added in vSphere API 7.0.2.0.
